title: BRIEF-Teva Announces Exclusive Launch Of Two Strengths Of A Generic Version Of Solodyn® In The United States
text: February 20, 2018 / 4:13 PM / Updated 23 minutes ago BRIEF-Teva Announces Exclusive Launch Of Two Strengths Of A Generic Version Of Solodyn® In The United States Reuters Staff 1 Min Read Feb 20 (Reuters) - Teva Pharmaceutical Industries Ltd: * TEVA ANNOUNCES EXCLUSIVE LAUNCH OF TWO STRENGTHS OF A GENERIC VERSION OF SOLODYN® IN THE UNITED STATES * TEVA - ‍EXCLUSIVE LAUNCH OF 2 STRENGTHS OF GENERIC VERSION OF SOLODYN (MINOCYCLINE HCL) EXTENDED RELEASE TABLETS, 65 AND 115 MG, IN U.S.​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
